body_html: Thanks Vincent. The issue was that I shouldn't have been using wget at all. I thought that would get me the 1_notmnist.ipynb file, but instead it downloaded the web page view of the 1_notmnist.ipynb file. I cloned the tensorflow repository, and opening the file in the repository worked just fine.
